sentences.en: Not surprisingly, the rich are better endowed than the poor, and the Kinh and Chinese population is better endowed than ethnic minorities.

sentences.en: Nature had endowed man with certain capabilities and endurances, which are not found in woman.

sentences.en: More endowed and prosperous local governments have tended to benefit more from the PAR process.

sentences.en: At the same time, it is easy to install and is rather well-endowed.
